               <msContents>
                  <summary>List of taxpayers; the payments were in wheat, barley and lentils</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; on the back P.Col. V 1 verso 5</note>
                     <note type="general">In general the names are in alphabetical order, with a few exceptions</note>
                     <note type="general">Some names are accompanied by check marks indicating that these people had paid</note>
                     <note type="general">There are several cases of payments with conversion from one type of produce to another</note>
                     <note type="general">The list was checked by an official who left some marginal notations</note>
                     <note type="general">13 cols. of writing, 11 of them in good condition; 18 lines in col. 1; 26 lines in col. 2; 20 in col. 3; 18 in col. 4; 17 in col. 5; 17 in col. 6; 14 in col. 7; 18 in col. 8; 22 in col 9; 18 in col. 10; 18 in col. 11; 18 in col. 12; only traces in col. 13</note>
